      "whyNow": "Ferritin 9 (ref 30–400) and you started iron ~4 weeks ago — worth confirming it's working",
      "person": "{{PERSON_SLUG}}", "priority": "medium", "kind": "get-more-data",
      "sourceCount": 2, "topTier": "T1" } ] }
